<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class= "interpreter-container">

      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
        <div class= "text-center">
          <%= image_tag 'leore.jpg', class: "profile-pic img-circle" %>
          <h1><%= @interpreter.name %></h1>
          <p>
            <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-star-half"></i>
          </p>
          <h2><%= Review.average_overall(@interpreter) %></h2>
        </div>
      </div>


      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
        <div class="interpreter-details">
          <h2>ABOUT</h2>
          <h2>Bio</h2> <p><%= truncate(@interpreter.bio, :length => 40, :separator => ' ')%></p>
          <h2>Location</h2> <p><%= @interpreter.location %></p>
          <h2>Price Per Hour</h2> <p><%= @interpreter.price %></p>
          <h2>Years Experience</h2> <p> <%= @interpreter.years_of_experience %></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
       <div class= "interpreter-booking">
        <h2>BOOKING FORM</h2>
        <%= render 'layouts/booking' %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class= "col-xs-8 col-sm-offset-4">
      <div class= "interpreter-availability">
        <h2>AVAILABILITY</h2>
        <br>

        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Asperiores, quisquam numquam. Quam sapiente suscipit, eaque et, perspiciatis cupiditate quos architecto beatae iusto, esse minus corporis est ab ea nobis libero.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class= "col-xs-8 col-sm-offset-4">
      <div class= "interpreter-reviews">

        <h2>REVIEWS</h2>

        <br>

        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Temporibus, ducimus recusandae tempore. Accusantium deserunt inventore consequuntur perspiciatis maxime quos, soluta quia sequi distinctio ut labore officiis, architecto dignissimos harum id.</p>

        <br>

        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Architecto dolorem optio, pariatur numquam ut, minus facere voluptatem voluptate temporibus molestias perspiciatis corporis esse doloribus velit, fugiat recusandae. Culpa, rem, eius.</p>

        <br>

        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. In vel suscipit culpa eius, veniam labore laboriosam nulla dolorum nostrum! Unde iste beatae, nesciunt quia commodi quod aliquam laudantium esse facilis.</p>


        <% @interpreter.reviews.all.each do |review| %>
        <ul>
          <p> Overall Performance: <%= review.overall_performance%> </p>
          <p> Language Skill: <%= review.language_skill%> |
            Friendliness: <%= review.friendliness%>|
            Professionalism: <%= review.professionalism%> |
            Punctuality: <%= review.punctuality%></p>
            <p> Description: <%= review.content%></p>
          </ul>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>


